  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nWe run multiple Erigon versions, as the infrastructure grows. We would like to be able to verify running Erigon version from outside via HTTP call.\r\n\r\nSomething a long the lines of:\r\n```\r\n$ curl -s 10.129.0.21:6060/debug/version\r\n404 page not found\r\n```\r\n\r\nand having there:\r\n- golang version used to compile\r\n- erigon version itself\r\n- any other information, especially at compile time, which would be useful for bug reports to Erigon devs themselves\r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\n\r\nDo you have ideas regarding the implementation of this feature?\r\n- No\r\n\r\nAre you willing to implement this feature?\r\n- Probably no",
